Tailwindcss
- npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
- npx tailwindcss init
- comply template
- add directives to bottom of index.css (not replace)
- modify app.jsx

Smart contract
- npm init -y

React Dependencies
- npm install react-icons ethers

